     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       mnmlst FAQs
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Sm frqntly skd qstns (FAQs) bt mnmlsm nd lvng th mnmlst lf, fr ths nw t th cncpt.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Why b  mnmlst?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: It’s  wy t scp th xcsss f th wrld rnd s — th xcsss f cnsmrsm, mtrl pssssns, clttr, hvng t mch t d, t mch dbt, t mny dstrctns, t mch ns. Bt t lttl mnng. Mnmlsm s  wy f schwng th nn-ssntl n rdr t fcs n wht’s trly mprtnt, wht gvs r lvs mnng, wht gvs s jy nd vl.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Isn’t mnmlsm brng r t sprs, wth nthng n yr lf?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: Ths s  mscncptn bt mnmlsm — tht t’s ncssrly mnk-lk, mpty, brng, strl. Nt t ll. Wll, t cn b, f y g n tht drctn, bt I dn’t dvct tht flvr f mnmlsm. Instd, w r clrng wy ll bt th mst ssntl thngs — t mk rm fr tht whch gvs s th mst jy. Clr wy th dstrctns s w cn crt smthng ncrdbl. Clr wy ll th blgtns s w cn spnd tm wth lvd ns. Clr wy th ns s w cn cncntrt n nnr pc, n sprtlty (f w wsh), n r thnkng. As  rslt, thr s mr hppnss, pc, nd jy, bcs w’v md rm fr ths thngs.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Wht s mnmlst lvng?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: It’s smply gttng rd f thngs y d nt s r nd, lvng n nclttrd, smpl nvrnmnt nd n nclttrd, smpl lf. It’s lvng wtht n bsssn wth mtrl thngs r n bsssn wth dng vrythng nd dng t mch. It’s sng smpl tls, hvng  smpl wrdrb, crryng lttl nd lvng lghtly.
       <br/>
       <span id="more-265">
       </span>
       <br/>
       <strong>
        Q: Wht r th bnfts f mnmlsm?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: Thr r mny. It’s lwr n strss. It’s lss xpnsv nd lss dbt. It’s lss clnng nd mntnng. It’s mr njybl. Thr’s mr rm fr crtng, fr lvd ns, fr pc, fr dng th thngs tht gv y jy. Thr’s mr tm fr gttng hlthy. It’s mr sstnbl. It’s sr t rgnz. Ths r nly th strt.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Wht ds th schdl f  mnmlst lk lk?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: Thr’s n sngl nswr t ths qstn, bt  mnmlst wld prbbly fcs n dng lss, n hvng  lss clttrd schdl, bt wht’s n hs r hr schdl wld b mprtnt. A mnmlst mght nt ctlly kp  schdl r clndr, t n xtrm, f h ddn’t hv mch t d ch dy — h mght nstd lv nd wrk mmnt-by-mmnt, r jst dcd ch mrnng t fcs n n r tw mprtnt thngs.
      </p>
      <p>
       A mnmlst wld ls sv  lt f tm bcs f hvng lss clttr nd fwr pssssns. Tht mns lss tm clnng nd mntnng, nd lss tm srchng fr thngs. A mnmlst wh clrs wy dstrctns nd
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2007/02/how-not-to-multitask-work-simpler-and/">
        sngl-tsks
       </a>
       wld ls wst lss tm wth ths dstrctns nd n swtchng bck nd frth btwn tsks (mlt-tskng).
      </p>
      <p>
       In gnrl, ll ths rslts n mr tm fr rlxng, fr hbbs, fr crtng, fr dng fn thngs.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Wht rls d I nd t fllw t bcm mnmlst?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: Thr r n st rls. Thr’s n n wy. Wht I sggst fr lvng mnmlly sn’t wht smn ls wld rcmmnd, nr s t hw y wld lv yr mnmlst lf. In gnrl, hwvr, y wnt t lv smply wtht t mny nncssry pssssns, dstrctns, clttr, r wst. Y wnt t lv frglly, dbt-fr, sstnbly, ntrlly.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: D y nd t b vgn r vgtrn t b mnmlst?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: N. Whl I blv th vgn/vgtrn lfstyl s cnsstnt wth mnmlsm, y cn t smply s n mnvr s wll. Agn, thr’s n n wy. A mnmlst wld try t t ntrlly, wtht t mch prcssng, nd nt t t mch fd (sch s th rdcls prtns t mst rstrnts ths dys).
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: I blv n smplfyng, bt why shld I b s frgl — wht wrng wth  fw
        <span class="caps">
         REALLY
        </span>
        nc thngs?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: Frglty s smply  wy f nt spndng n nncssry thngs — stckng t th ssntls. Is thr nythng wrng wth  fw rlly nc thngs? Nt ncssrly. If y nd t by smthng, t’s slly bttr t g fr qlty, rthr thn chp, bcs t’s bttr md nd wll lst lngr. Mnmlsm s bt qlty vr qntty.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hwvr … t’s lwys gd t xmn whthr t’s gd t hv n ttchmnt t mtrl thngs. Ths sn’t smthng I’v cmpltly sccdd wth — I lv my Mc, fr xmpl — bt t’s smthng I’v bn wrkng n. I m mch lss ttchd t pssssns thn I ws jst  fw yrs g, nd I rcmmnd tht vryn xmn thr rltnshp wth physcl thngs, wth prdcts, nd s f t’s rlly wht thy wnt.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Wht bt fndng mnmlsm n Amrc — whr y nd t hv  cr nd  jb?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: Ths whl st s bt fndng mnmlsm wthn th Amrcn cltr nd scty — s wll s thr ndstrlzd ntns — nt n sm rmt dsrt slnd. Th cmplxts nd scl xpcttns f th Untd Stts (nd thr ndstrlzd cntrs) s xctly why mnmlsm s ndd. All th dvc I gv n ths st (nd
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net">
        Zn Hbts
       </a>
       ) s md t ppl n ths mdrn scts.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’v lvd  mnmlst lf n Gm, nd nw n Sn Frncsc. It’s  mttr f chcs.
      </p>
      <p>
       D y nd t b s mnmlst s m, r smn lvng n th wldrnss? Nt t ll. It’s nt bt tht. It’s bt fndng smplcty nd fndng wht’s mprtnt t y, nd mkng chcs, rthr thn dptng th cnsmrst mndst tht mst ppl hv.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Arn’t y bng cntrdctry by clmng t b  mnmlst nd wnng  Mc, r  hs, r hvng sx kds?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: Agn, thr’s n n wy. Evryn mst fnd hs wn pth, nd mn s dffrnt thn wht smn ls wld cnsdr mnmlst. Als, I hv nvr clmd t b prfct – I’m strvng fr mnmlsm, bt I lwys hv rm fr mprvmnt. I hv thngs tht r ncnsstnt wth mnmlsm, r t lst by th dfntn f thrs. I’m wrkng n t.
      </p>
      <p>
       I shld sy  wrd r tw bt hvng sx kds nd mnmlsm. Hvng sx chldrn s ncnsstnt wth my mssg f smplfyng, frglty, dwnszng, bng grn.
      </p>
      <p>
       I dn’t hv  dfns – bt I d hv n xplntn fr th ncnsstncy. I hd my kds bfr (nd drng) my chng n phlsphy. In fct, my phlsphy s vlvng vn nw, s I cn’t clm t hv blvd n th thngs I blv n nw, fr  vry lng tm. Mny thngs I blv n r nly rcnt dvlpmnts.
      </p>
      <p>
       As n xmpl – nly rcntly, I md th dcsn t trnstn bck nt vgnsm (I ws vgn nc, bt hv bn lct-v vgg fr vr  yr). Bt I wn  pr f lthr sndls – d I thrw thm t? Wldn’t tht b wstfl? Is t bttr t b wstfl bt cnsstnt wth my blfs? It’s hrd t sy.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hwvr, I hv dcdd t wld b mst nthcl fr m t thrw t my chldrn, jst bcs I nw blv n dwnszng. It ws  tgh dcsn, bt I’m stckng by t.
      </p>
      <p>
       As  rslt f my smplfyng, I m bl t njy my tm wth my chldrn, nd I hv t dmt, thy r th bst thng t hppn t m. I dn’t rgrt hvng thm n bt, vn f thy r ncnsstnt wth my phlsphy f dwnszng.
      </p>
      <p>
       On th gd sd, I blv tht vn wth sx kds — bng vgn, byng lss stff, bng nrgy cnscs, gng cr-lss, wlkng mr fr trnsprttn – I ctlly s fwr rsrcs thn th vrg prsn n dvlpd cntrs (nd fr lss thn th vrg Amrcn) – ths s ccrdng t nln crbn ftprnt clcltrs. It’s nt  jstfctn fr hvng sx kds, bt jst  nt tht thngs rn’t s bd s thy cld b.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Why dn’t y hv  cmmnt bttn r cmmnts n ths st?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: I prpsly ddn’t ncld cmmnts n ths st fr  cpl f rsns:
      </p>
      <p>
       1. I lrdy mng svrl thr blgs, nd gt  tn f cmmnts t
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net">
        Zn Hbts
       </a>
       , nd hvng t mng nthr blg’s cmmnts s t mch fr m. I jst dn’t hv th tm, nd f I hd t d t, I cldn’t d ths blg.
      </p>
      <p>
       2. I lv dlg wth rdrs — t’s wht mks blggng sch  jy — bt cmmntng sn’t th nly wy. I ncrg y t rply t m bt ny f ths psts v
       <a href="http://twitter.com/zen_habits">
        Twttr
       </a>
       r n yr blg. Th dlg thn wll b lss lcl nd mr wdsprd.
      </p>
      <p>
       3. I lk th d f kpng thngs smpl n  blg bt mnmlsm.
      </p>
      <p>
       <strong>
        Q: Hw s mnmlst.cm dffrnt thn
        <a href="http://zenhabits.net">
         Zn Hbts
        </a>
        ?
       </strong>
      </p>
      <p>
       A: Wll, Zn Hbts s bt smplcty, nd mnmlst.cm s bt mnmlsm — cn’t y s th dffrnc?
      </p>
      <p>
       Srsly, thgh, thr wll b  dffrnt fcs hr thn t Zn Hbts, whch cvrs  wd rng f tpcs bsds smplcty, ncldng prdctvty, chngng hbts, hlth &amp; ftnss, fmly, fnncs, hppnss, nd ys, smplcty.
      </p>
      <p>
       Ths blg wll fcs prtty mch xclsvly n mnmlsm,  pssn f mn. Nt ll Zn Hbts rdrs r ncrdbly ntrstd n mnmlsm, s I’m brkng ff ths blg fr ths wh r.
      </p>
      <p>
       <em>
        If y hv thr qstns tht I shld ncld hr, pls
        <a href="http://twitter.com/zen_habits">
         lt m knw n Twttr
        </a>
        !
       </em>
      </p>
